<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TolE099">
<l>aṇṇañ cērnta miṭaṟṟeḻu vaḷiyicai</l>
<l>kaṇṇuṟ ṟaṭaiya yakāram piṟakkum</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l><foreign xml:lang="ta">y</foreign> is produced when the air arising in the throat</l>
<l>reaches the palate [and] the place is choked up.<note place="foot">This curious statement probably means a very close passing of the air-stream so that a kind of friction arises against the palate.</note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
